{"tid":1502070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"825 揸春袋","createTime":"2019-08-24T14:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T15:59:08.000Z","uid":25748,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a02356217f8cd9c1e747bb5cc831b7eb52f43ce8","tid":1502070,"uid":25748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"我屌爆你地老母講左好多次要揸春袋先有用係都要留戀街頭戰做乜撚野<br />\n有不對通知書又點 每一次街頭戰都有手足受傷送頭,而家唔係要放棄葵荃區手足而係集中人力做一啲港共政權驚嘅事<br />\n唔好再話咩之後再入機場, 812之後嘅813有幾多人入機場大家心照, 點解唔食住今日道火聽日一齊揸爆佢老母閪春袋<br />\n春袋範圍始終有外國旅客啲狗用得武力好有限大家明唔明"},{"pid":"f14cb0cd4c079594f53875ecad8f701410f544cf","tid":1502070,"uid":48081,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"星期日冇貨運你揸邊撚個春袋"},{"pid":"c0094d3bb000107438ed23574156968718a50a97","tid":1502070,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">825星期日<br />\n荃葵青/機場</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEhtr7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEhtr7b.png&h=d0ab0272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港，時代革命</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" cla